Author: ilovemargo
Text: Hey we're twinning! Except I could really go for a good poop.

Author: lavendermyth
Text: I think that reaction is pretty normal. I was told by one of my therapists at like age 16 that I had PTSD and I was like 'well that's just not possible because I haven't experienced any trauma' despite the fact that she was a trauma therapist that I was seeing for my multiple traumas.
